Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\shad0\fs28\pos(290,200)}開羅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿越沙特阿拉伯的喬斯達一行四人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正渡過紅海 準備進入埃及
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 老頭 有些不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方向錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道不是應該筆直朝西 向著埃及前進嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你好像要去那座島
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由於某些原因 之前沒告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在進入埃及前我要稍微繞點路 為了見某個人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對這趟旅途而言 他是至關重要的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至關重要的人物？
Comment: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(ED)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:15.11,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be1}All the old paintings on the tombs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:17.12,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be1}They do the sand dance Don't you know
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.43,0:22:18.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be1}If they move too quick
